Yep its true, why you ask? It doesnt cast<br>
Yeah thats right. the 56 decoy pet doesnt waste time casting DDs on targets, meaning what you ask? Well i Play on a pvp server(tallon zek) so pvp is a constant for me. 56pet+sow(or the best mage pet speed spell you have) means a nonstop hitting machine againts anyone. If you have a problem with people running from you all the time this pet is the best thing ever. Plus, let a 56pet put up its DS, and have it go toe to toe with an epic pet, 56 pet wins. Why? the epic pet kills itself on the 56 decoy pets dmg shield.<br>
<br>
Just a lil info on pvp, from a pvp mage<br>
Char is main pvp spell, Sirroco is a good opening spell, if you can get it off without them noticing.<br>
Mala type spells, dont waste your time unless its mala, everything else gets resisted. <p>Gnome of Tallon Zek</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27>Player vs Player</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
